                        <note rend="inline" type="source">493.11/897: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-02-26T16:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">February 26,
                                        1923—4 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>39. Your 65, February 23, noon.</p>
                        <p>You are authorized to join your colleagues in signing note.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
